item.title: A Brief Intro
item.description: Hello! My name is Jinny Gui, and I am a senior undergrad at Cornell University. I study Electrical and Computer Engineering (ECE) and minor in Computer Science (CS). My interests lie within robotics, computer vision, automation, and a general passion for efficiency and social good through a variety of different projects. Although I have done 3 summers of research with the Computer Systems Laboratory, I am now focused on industry and directly impacting the world around me.
